            "title": "財經｜SpaceX有權今年以600億美元收購Cursor  馬斯克xAI編程追趕",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜SpaceX有權今年以600億美元收購Cursor 馬斯克xAI編程追趕\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜SpaceX有權今年以600億美元收購Cursor 馬斯克xAI編程追趕</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"s1\">SpaceX宣布與AI編程初創Cursor（母公司Anysphere）達成協議，獲得今年稍後以600億美元（約4680億港元）全資收購權利，若放棄則支付100億美元（約780億港元）合作費用，創企業史上最大「分手費」紀錄。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"s1\">雙方正密切合作打造「全球最佳程式設計與知識工作AI」，結合Cursor自動編碼技術同SpaceX百萬級H100等效Colossus超算，強化xAI在AI編程領域競爭力。 </span></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"s1\">馬斯克早前承認xAI喺編程工具落後OpenAI及Anthropic，呢筆交易正值SpaceX、xAI同X平台業務組合備受關注IPO前夕，Cursor去年秋季融資估值已達500億美元，自動編碼平台成長迅速，吸引眾多開發者。</span></p></div>",
